FBIS4-61982 "drsov092_r_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 Azerbaijan Surprise Armenian Artillery Attack Inflicts `Heavy Losses' Surprise Armenian Artillery Attack Inflicts `Heavy Losses' LD1105201394 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1940 GMT 11 May 94 LD1105201394 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] An unexpected artillery attack by Armenian armed formations in the west of Azerbaijan has caused heavy losses in units of the Azerbaijani Army that were not prepared for it. Independent sources report that over 60,000 civilian refugees are now urgently leaving the area of the front that is near the administrative center of Akveri.
